column5: I hope you have a super day!  OK now what did the Geek getcha?
Have a GREAT day dear !
Maybe he buggered off and gave her peace and quiet for a day. Happy birthday, Nique!
Happy Birthday and have a great one Monique, hope he gets you something reeeally nice.
Cool, its also my birthday today!  happy birthday, hope its a great one
And a Happy Happy to you too, Kemper!
Happy Birthday Monique     I certainly hope that guy is taking you out for dinner tonight!!  Happy birthday Kemper!  Joey
Happy Birthday Monique & Kemper!
Happy Birthday Monique & Kemper!  Hope you both are having a great one!
Hey Monique and Kemper, Happy Happy, hope you both had a great day!!!
Happy birthday Monique and Kemper All the best to ya's Leechman
Happy belated Monique. So do tell us, what did he do for you?  Happy belated to you too Kemper.
Thanks Everyone  And Happy B-Day Kemper!!!  I got a dozen beautiful red roses and a trip to Cuba.  We are leaving on the 7th.  I wish it was my B-Day everyday.
Dang Cuba that sounds nice now where are ya setting up the tent LOL  Happy Belated B day Mrs BOSS have a fun and safe trip
Have a great day both of you guys....
Happy belated birthday!!  Hope you have a great time in Cuba!!!  You too Kemper....except for the cuba thing....LOL

Just remember TJ..it is acceptable in many Carribean countries for women to go topless..however it may not be a good idea for you to do it. There are poachers and you may be mistaken for a bear or Cupra Chabra or something.
Happy Birthday gal!!!
A trip to Cuba. Do you need some company,or you taking the old man.  Happy birthday
No.. my Dad is staying here... but IM going!!
